576
01:11:12,052 --> 01:11:14,972
Uzmi sve.

577
01:11:32,073 --> 01:11:34,366
Ti ces se vratiti zar ne?

578
01:11:34,492 --> 01:11:37,495
Ne znam.

579
01:11:37,620 --> 01:11:41,957
Mi moramo postovati zakone
na koje smo se zakleli.

580
01:11:42,124 --> 01:11:45,044
Znam da se mozda necu vratiti.

581
01:11:45,920 --> 01:11:49,340
I znam da me nista na ovom svetu
nemoze zadrzati.

582
01:12:00,768 --> 01:12:03,395
Vratio sam se lutko.

583
01:12:03,562 --> 01:12:05,606
Oh, Dzeri!

584
01:12:07,566 --> 01:12:10,402
