606
01:13:43,913 --> 01:13:46,040
Ona je moja zena

607
01:13:46,165 --> 01:13:49,460
i ja kazem da ide.

608
01:13:58,636 --> 01:14:02,098
Ako neide ona, ne idem ni ja.

609
01:14:22,076 --> 01:14:24,954
U redu je gospodjo ona je moja zena.

610
01:14:25,704 --> 01:14:30,251
Mozda ako mi neko kupi verenicki prsten
ljudi nebi tako buljili.

611
01:14:30,376 --> 01:14:33,462
Idem da razgovaram sa mamom..
Hej, oseti ovo.

612
01:14:37,133 --> 01:14:42,346
Lutko, kupi cu ti najlepsi
verenicki prsten u Londonu.

613
01:14:48,144 --> 01:14:50,187
Mrzim ovo cekanje.

614
01:14:50,354 --> 01:14:52,731
Nisam cuo da se zalis kada su
dolazili slobodoumnici.

615
01:14:52,898 --> 01:14:57,153
Oh, look here. You're not suggesting
that an artiste of Liberace's stature

616
01:14:57,278 --> 01:15:01,824
